Module net.etf.project
Package net.etf.project.model.vehicles

Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
net.etf.project.model.vehicles.Vehicle
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, ICharging
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bicycle, Car, Scooter
public abstract class Vehicle extends Object implements ICharging, Serializable
Represents an abstract base class for all vehicles in the system. Implements ICharging for battery charging functionality and Serializable for object serialization. Each vehicle has a unique ID, purchase price, manufacturer, model, battery level, a list of malfunctions, and repair costs.
